Michael L. MCDONALD and Point Break Group Management, LLC, Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
CITY OF WILDWOOD, Defendant-Respondent. C-700 September Term 2018
082258 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000109-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
